column1: #Text=An American War Steamer off the Irish Coast.
#Text=—The United States war frigate Canadiagua arrived at Kingston yesterday from Queenstown.
#Text=Seizure op War Ships in the Thames.
#Text=—The Shipping Gazette says it is reported that Government has seized the Spanish ironclads fitting out in the Thames ; also the steamer Sirius fitting out for the republic of Columbia.
#Text=Benjamin Coleman surrendered at the Central Criminal Couit yesterday to take his trial for libel concerning Mr.
#Text=Application was made for the postponement of the trial, on the ground that it was necessary to procure witnesses from New York, the libel having been copied from a paper published in that city.
#Text=The deputyrecorder refused the application for the postponement, and the trial was fixed for Saturday (to-morrow).
